'''Warro Field''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on the [[Hapan]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Terephon]]. It was used by the planetary militia as a base from which to launch their [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]], which by [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] were outdated [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunters]].

